<br>
I have a Centi Warhammer that I truly do love, but is there something better out there that can be quested or saved up for? I love hitting for a solid 30 every time I swing my warhammer, but as I learn more about playing a cleric, it is easy to see that I serve the group better when I am out of the battle, casting or medding. It would seem obvious that there must be other weapons out there that will give me a stat boost or an effect, I just don't know of any.<br>
<br>
